{"tid":1422213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"交通燈剪線全部係示威者做?","createTime":"2019-08-06T10:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:23:20.000Z","uid":265268,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"43e0227064dd3b1e4b1953d7844340eafa247e0e","tid":1422213,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:07:45.000Z","msg":"根據新聞及連登資訊, 今日以下地點交通燈失靈:<br />\n新界: 屯門, 沙田, 將軍澳<br />\n九龍: 荃灣, 大窩口, 長沙灣, 深水埗, 旺角, 油麻地, 佐敦, 尖沙咀, 牛頭角, 觀塘<br />\n港島: 灣仔, 銅鑼灣, 砲台山, 北角<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果全部係義士做, 小弟配服  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過示威者可以 pull out 咁大規模破壞, 又冇黑警周, 有啲不可思議...<br />\n時間上都有啲奇, 不合作運動明明要罷工前做, 而家係罷工後.<br />\n交通狗又配合地縮9哂, 由佢亂 (雖然 turn out 都唔係好亂)<br />\n<br />\n翻查連登, 只有一位新用戶 <span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚起我底 #289535</span> 曾力推將交通燈<span style=\"color: red;\">整爛/拆/噴漆/剪電線</span>, 有過千like. 而佢係冇任何其他發言.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1400171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1400171</a><br />\n其他連登仔係講噴黑, 冇呢位用戶咁癲.<br />\n<br />\n今日周保松分析林奠記招, 新玩法係要煲大香港好危險, 政府同警方就可以順理成章&quot;平亂&quot;.<br />\n我又見到呢幾日黑社會出動, 各區大量無謂TG...<br />\n所以我會懷疑係對家做緊某種效果 <br />\n(利申: 如果義士做, 本人致歉, 絕不割蓆!)"},{"pid":"bde37df4e82fb8fae88bc5d8dccde4c6ce05a30f","tid":1422213,"uid":41308,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"根本無人整爛 係政府專登熄燈"},{"pid":"55b8c62ffa876e67e46aa84d8c835a6f7c0d3152","tid":1422213,"uid":247931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:17:47.000Z","msg":"一定係鬼"},{"pid":"57791f6415d6364c37a91c5ff5ce640c32c58e0a","tid":1422213,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"[懶人包]黑警記者會重點及拆招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08e23e98d1a5b30efec975678b840d73930ed6ce","tid":1422213,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"落場睇下咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb2f89950d107c508316c5e69bd7c6070e20b35","tid":1422213,"uid":72795,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"好鬼 想掘人出嚟？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府自己熄燈</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6e0a6f844da1a8d913f85fb9ffe83ea2cc1190d9","tid":1422213,"uid":83602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"咁好幻想力<br />\n啲野用得耐咪壞囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a52f2af6bc853a4c8406ffd7e1d8b5661ef5de","tid":1422213,"uid":137981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"我都認同好鬼， 有d燈根本都無明顯開過蓋，粒螺絲都仲有油漆封住。<br />\n 再加上開個蓋又要螺絲批， 又要cut鉗<br />\n真係咁多人會帶係身？"},{"pid":"c15fa91970e16490c37fe89ac413f25ee4df8dce","tid":1422213,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDXnjAy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDXnjAy.jpg&h=15176b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/60-kg/_/R-p-187036?mc=8484823&amp;c=%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fp%2F60-kg%2F_%2FR-p-187036%3Fmc%3D8484823%26c%3D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%2589%25B2&d=Lhg6HStjEOrAYLon%2F%2F44J5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=c6c6adb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/p/60-kg/_/R-p-187036?mc=8484823&amp;c=%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2</a>"},{"pid":"5cac3cc